headline: Paychex (PAYX): Assessing Valuation After Recent Share Price Dip
summary: Paychex (PAYX) remains in focus as investors assess the company’s returns in a shifting market environment. The stock has seen a dip over the past month, which has prompted questions about its current valuation. See our latest analysis for Paychex. Despite slipping 2.9% over the past month and recently trading at $124.6, Paychex’s share price has actually drifted lower for most of this year.
